    "name": "Smart Hospital Management System API",
    "description": "Postman collection for all Spring Boot REST APIs in the Smart Hospital Management System. Uses HTTP Basic auth with collection variables. Default credentials are admin/admin123; change username/password to doctor/doctor123, nurse/nurse123, or receptionist/reception123 when testing role-specific access.",
